rows.label: qst710702_msg0001
rows.name: Have you procured any good items, mo?

rows.label: qst710702_msg0101
rows.name:
We did it, mo! We've finally
reached 500 MnP, mo!

rows.label: qst710702_msg0102
rows.name:
If we convert this to G, it'll
be 1 million G in total, mo!

rows.label: qst710702_msg0103
rows.name:
Now, Momimi will quickly turn
these goods into money and give
it to the big person, mo.

rows.label: qst710702_msg0104
rows.name:
Mo? You don't know who the big person
is, mo? Of course, it's the one I'm
lending 1 million G to, mo!

rows.label: qst710702_msg0105
rows.name:
Apparently, the big person
is lavishing gifts on some
girl somewhere, mo!

rows.label: qst710702_msg0106
rows.name:
He plans to give her the entire
1 million G this time, so he
must be really into her, mo.

rows.label: qst710702_msg0108
rows.name:
...Well then, thank you, mo!
You've been a great help, mo!

rows.label: qst710702_msg0109
rows.name:
Please continue to support the
Pyrithium Trade Guild, mo!

rows.label: qst710702_msg0202
rows.name:
Go find more things that people
would want to collect, mo!

rows.label: qst710702_msg0203
rows.name:
Especially the Bunnit Bunnymeat
from the monsters in Gula is
traded at a high price, mo!

rows.label: qst710702_msg0204
rows.name:
If you bring me that, I'll
exchange it for a good amount
of MnP... "Momimi's Points," mo!
